    "question_id" : 8512121,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Why not get what you are looking for from the get go and read a string from the file instead of an array of bytes?  Something like:</p>\n\n<pre><code>BufferedReader in = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader( new FileInputStream( \"foo.txt\"), Charset.forName( \"UTF-8\"));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>then readLine from in until it's done.</p>\n"
